{"id":54,"parent_id":30,"book_id":95,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":54,"title":"2 Nephi 24","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Ne.","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 24"],[".studySummary",["i","Israel will be gathered and will enjoy millennial rest—Lucifer was cast out of heaven for rebellion—Israel will triumph over Babylon (the world)—Compare",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/14"},"Isaiah 14"],". About 559–545",["span.small","B.C."]]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.1","order":"05.13.024.5641"},["b","1"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"For"],"the Lord will have mercy on Jacob, and will yet",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"choose"],"Israel, and set them in their own land; and the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"strangers"],"shall be joined with them, and they shall cleave to the house of Jacob."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.2","order":"05.13.024.5642"},["b","2"],"And the people shall take them and bring them to their place; yea, from far unto the ends of the earth; and they shall return to their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"lands of promise"],". And the house of Israel shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"possess"],"them, and the land of the Lord shall be for",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"servants"],"and handmaids; and they shall take them captives unto whom they were captives; and they shall",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_2d"},"rule"],"over their oppressors."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.3","order":"05.13.024.5643"},["b","3"],"And it shall come to pass in that day that the Lord shall give thee",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"rest"],", from thy sorrow, and from thy fear, and from the hard bondage wherein thou wast made to serve."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.4","order":"05.13.024.5644"},["b","4"],"And it shall come to pass in that day, that thou shalt take up this proverb",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"against"],"the king of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"Babylon"],", and say: How hath the oppressor ceased, the golden city ceased!"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.5","order":"05.13.024.5645"},["b","5"],"The Lord hath broken the staff of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"wicked"],", the scepters of the rulers."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.6","order":"05.13.024.5646"},["b","6"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"He"],"who smote the people in wrath with a continual stroke, he that ruled the nations in anger, is persecuted, and none hindereth."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.7","order":"05.13.024.5647"},["b","7"],"The whole earth is at",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"rest"],", and is quiet; they break forth into",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"singing"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.8","order":"05.13.024.5648"},["b","8"],"Yea, the fir trees rejoice at thee, and also the cedars of Lebanon, saying: Since thou art laid down no feller is come up against us."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.9","order":"05.13.024.5649"},["b","9"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"Hell"],"from beneath is moved for thee to meet thee at thy coming; it stirreth up the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"dead"],"for thee, even all the chief ones of the earth; it hath raised up from their thrones all the kings of the nations."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.10","order":"05.13.024.5650"},["b","10"],"All they shall speak and say unto thee: Art thou also become weak as we? Art thou become like unto us?"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.11","order":"05.13.024.5651"},["b","11"],"Thy pomp is brought down to the grave; the noise of thy viols is not heard; the worm is spread under thee, and the worms cover thee."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.12","order":"05.13.024.5652"},["b","12"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"How"],"art thou fallen from heaven, O",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"Lucifer"],", son of the morning! Art thou cut down to the ground, which did weaken the nations!"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.13","order":"05.13.024.5653"},["b","13"],"For thou hast said in thy heart:",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"I"],"will ascend into heaven, I will exalt my throne above the stars of God; I will sit also upon the mount of the congregation, in the sides of the north;"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.14","order":"05.13.024.5654"},["b","14"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"I"],"will ascend above the heights of the clouds; I will be like the Most High."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.15","order":"05.13.024.5655"},["b","15"],"Yet thou shalt be brought down to hell, to the sides of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"pit"],"."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.16","order":"05.13.024.5656"},["b","16"],"They that see thee shall narrowly look upon thee, and shall consider thee, and shall say: Is this the man that made the earth to tremble, that did shake kingdoms?"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.17","order":"05.13.024.5657"},["b","17"],"And made the world as a wilderness, and destroyed the cities thereof, and opened not the house of his prisoners?"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.18","order":"05.13.024.5658"},["b","18"],"All the kings of the nations, yea, all of them, lie in glory, every one of them in his own house."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.19","order":"05.13.024.5659"},["b","19"],"But thou art cast out of thy grave like an abominable branch, and the remnant of those that are slain, thrust through with a sword, that go down to the stones of the pit; as a carcass trodden under feet."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.20","order":"05.13.024.5660"},["b","20"],"Thou shalt not be joined with them in burial, because thou hast destroyed thy land and slain thy people; the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"seed"],"of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"evil-doers"],"shall never be renowned."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.21","order":"05.13.024.5661"},["b","21"],"Prepare slaughter for his children for the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"iniquities"],"of their fathers, that they do not rise, nor possess the land, nor fill the face of the world with cities."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.22","order":"05.13.024.5662"},["b","22"],"For I will rise up against them, saith the Lord of Hosts, and cut off from Babylon the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"name"],", and remnant, and son, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"nephew"],", saith the Lord."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.23","order":"05.13.024.5663"},["b","23"],"I will also make it a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"possession"],"for the bittern, and pools of water; and I will sweep it with the besom of destruction, saith the Lord of Hosts."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.24","order":"05.13.024.5664"},["b","24"],"The Lord of Hosts hath sworn, saying: Surely as I have thought, so shall it come to pass; and as I have purposed, so shall it stand—"],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.25","order":"05.13.024.5665"},["b","25"],"That I will bring the Assyrian in my land, and upon my mountains tread him under foot; then shall his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"yoke"],"depart from off them, and his burden depart from off their shoulders."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.26","order":"05.13.024.5666"},["b","26"],"This is the purpose that is purposed upon the whole earth; and this is the hand that is stretched out upon all nations."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.27","order":"05.13.024.5667"},["b","27"],"For the Lord of Hosts hath purposed, and who shall disannul? And his hand is stretched out, and who shall turn it back?"],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.28","order":"05.13.024.5668"},["b","28"],"In the year that king",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"Ahaz"],"died was this burden."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.29","order":"05.13.024.5669"},["b","29"],"Rejoice not thou, whole Palestina, because the rod of him that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"smote"],"thee is broken; for out of the serpent’s root shall come forth a cockatrice, and his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_29b"},"fruit"],"shall be a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_29c"},"fiery flying serpent"],"."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.30","order":"05.13.024.5670"},["b","30"],"And the firstborn of the poor shall feed, and the needy shall lie down in safety; and I will kill thy root with famine, and he shall slay thy remnant."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.31","order":"05.13.024.5671"},["b","31"],"Howl, O gate; cry, O city; thou, whole Palestina, art dissolved; for there shall come from the north a smoke, and none shall be alone in his appointed times."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.32","order":"05.13.024.5672"},["b","32"],"What shall then answer the messengers of the nations? That the Lord hath founded",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_32a"},"Zion"],", and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_32b"},"poor"],"of his people shall trust in it."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.1a","order":"05.13.024.5673"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/14.1.1-32"},"Isa. 14:1 (1–32)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.1b","order":"05.13.024.5675"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.17"},"Zech. 1:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/2.12"},"2:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.1c","order":"05.13.024.5677"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/60.3.3-5,10"},"Isa. 60:3 (3–5, 10)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/stranger"},"TG Stranger"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.2a","order":"05.13.024.5679"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/promised-lands"},"TG Promised Lands"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.2b","order":"05.13.024.5681"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.12"},"Amos 9:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.2c","order":"05.13.024.5683"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/60.14.10-12,14"},"Isa. 60:14 (10–12, 14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.2d","order":"05.13.024.5685"},["b","2d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/kingdom-of-god-on-earth"},"TG Kingdom of God, on Earth"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.3a","order":"05.13.024.5687"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.13"},"Josh. 1:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.24"},"D&C 84:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.4a","order":"05.13.024.5689"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.6.6-8"},"Hab. 2:6 (6–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.4b","order":"05.13.024.5691"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/babylon"},"TG Babylon"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.5a","order":"05.13.024.5693"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/earth-cleansing-of"},"TG Earth, Cleansing of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/wickedness"},"Wickedness"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.6a","order":"05.13.024.5695"},["b","6a"],["span.small","IE"],"Babylon."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.7a","order":"05.13.024.5697"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/earth-renewal-of"},"TG Earth, Renewal of"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.7b","order":"05.13.024.5699"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/55.12.12-13"},"Isa. 55:12 (12–13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.9a","order":"05.13.024.5701"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/32.21"},"Ezek. 32:21"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hell"},"TG Hell"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.9b","order":"05.13.024.5703"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spirits-in-prison"},"TG Spirits in Prison"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.12a","order":"05.13.024.5705"},["b","12a"],["span.small","IE"],"The fallen king of Babylon is typified by the fallen “son of the morning,” Lucifer in",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.12-15"},"vv. 12–15"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.26"},"D&C 76:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.12b","order":"05.13.024.5707"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/devil"},"TG Devil"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.13a","order":"05.13.024.5709"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/4.1.1-4"},"Moses 4:1 (1–4)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.14a","order":"05.13.024.5711"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/2.4"},"2 Thes. 2:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.15a","order":"05.13.024.5713"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/28.1"},"Ps. 28:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/88.4"},"88:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.3"},"1 Ne. 14:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.20a","order":"05.13.024.5715"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/21.10.10-11"},"Ps. 21:10 (10–11)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/37.28"},"37:28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/109.13"},"109:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.20b","order":"05.13.024.5717"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/wickedness"},"TG Wickedness"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.21a","order":"05.13.024.5719"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/20.5"},"Ex. 20:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.22a","order":"05.13.024.5721"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/10.7"},"Prov. 10:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/51.62"},"Jer. 51:62"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.22b","order":"05.13.024.5723"},["b","22b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/job/18.19"},"Job 18:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.23a","order":"05.13.024.5725"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.11.11-15"},"Isa. 34:11 (11–15)"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.25a","order":"05.13.024.5727"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.27"},"Isa. 10:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.28a","order":"05.13.024.5729"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/16.20"},"2 Kgs. 16:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.29a","order":"05.13.024.5731"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/26.6"},"2 Chr. 26:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"29b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.29b","order":"05.13.024.5733"},["b","29b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/18.8.1,8"},"2 Kgs. 18:8 (1, 8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"29c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.29c","order":"05.13.024.5735"},["b","29c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-types-of-in-anticipation"},"TG Jesus Christ, Types of, in Anticipation"],"."],["div",{"id":"32a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.32a","order":"05.13.024.5737"},["b","32a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/zion"},"TG Zion"],"."],["div",{"id":"32b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.32b","order":"05.13.024.5739"},["b","32b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.12"},"Zeph. 3:12"],"."]]}
